patch.comment: Add `"node"` condition before `"import"` in the `"exports"` map so that Node.js uses the CJS output (which handles extensionless imports), while bundlers still use ESM via `"import"`. Fixes https://github.com/microsoft/rushstack/issues/5644.
Publish patch release because dependencies of 2.2.0 were incorrectly published.

minor.comment: Normalize package layout. CommonJS is now under `lib-commonjs`, DTS is now under `lib-dts`, and ESM is now under `lib-esm`. Imports to `lib` still work as before, handled by the `"exports"` field in `package.json`.

patch.comment: Use pnpm dependency path implementation from `@rushstack/rush-pnpm-kit-v8`

major.comment: Add support for PNPM 10 lockfile format

patch.comment: Numerous improvements to the lockfile parser
Bump "express" to 4.21.1 to address reported vulnerabilities in 4.20.0.
Upgraded `js-yaml` dependency
Improve support for PNPM lockfile format V6.0
Refactoring to support future work
Update documentation for `extends`

minor.comment: Update to use a new API from rush-sdk.

patch.comment: Include CHANGELOG.md in published releases again
Update the exit code to 0 for `lockfile-explorer --help`.
Fix some issues when parsing certain lockfile syntaxes

minor.comment: Add `--subspace` command-line parameter to support Rush subspaces

patch.comment: Replace the dependency on the `colors` package with `Colorize` from `@rushstack/terminal`.
Fix line endings in published package.
Update type-only imports to include the type modifier.

minor.comment: Add support for the V6 lockfile used by PNPM 8.

patch.comment: Support context parameter in pnpmfile readPackage

major.comment: Initial feature-complete release of Lockfile Explorer

patch.comment: Fix an issue with the tab component
Fix an issue where the upgrade notice wasn't displayed until after pressing CTRL+C
Fix a regression where some CSS styles were not being loaded properly

minor.comment: Add "lfx" as an alias for the "lockfile-explorer" shell command

patch.comment: Add some basic command-line help and improve some message strings
Add support for rush components
Print an upgrade notice when there is a newer release of the @rushstack/lockfile-explorer package
Fix an issue where an Error is thrown when a pnpmfile does not exist.
Lockfile Explorer now displays a disconnection message if the client / server is disconnected
Fix an issue where some assets were not packaged in the production release

minor.comment: Fixed issues related to influencer resolution in lockfile explorer; Cleaned up UI & improved UX.

patch.comment: The CLI now supports a "--debug" parameter for troubleshooting
Initial preview release
